wmii-session

deps
====
wmii, task, vim, surfraw, tabbed, surf, zathura, urxvt


install
=======
copy session.sh to ~/.wmii
copy wmii-session to PATH
or try the sample wmiirc_local


bashrc
======

alias vim='vim --servername "$(wmiir cat /tag/sel/ctl | head -n 1)"'

opdf() {
	if [[ $@ =~ ^\/ ]]; then
		cmd="OpenPDF $@"
	else
		cmd="OpenPDF $(pwd)/$@"
	fi
	wmiir xwrite /event "$cmd"
}

ourl() {
	if [ -f "$@" ]; then
		cmd="file\:\/\/$@"
	else
		cmd="OpenURL $@"
	fi
	wmiir xwrite /event "$cmd"
}

notes
=====

addpath works only from cli
